hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 对于一个纯洛伦兹变换，其矩阵元满足
$$
\Lambda^0_{\ 0}=\gamma,\quad
\Lambda^0_{\ i}=-\gamma\beta_i,\quad
\Lambda^i_{\ 0}=-\gamma\beta_i,\quad
\Lambda^i_{\ j}=\delta^i_j+(\gamma-1)\hat\beta^i\hat\beta_j\,.
$$
2. 根据给定的矩阵，
$$
\Lambda^0_{\ 0}=\frac{5}{3}\;\Longrightarrow\;\gamma=\frac{5}{3},
$$
$$
\Lambda^0_{\ 1}=-\gamma\,\beta_x=-\frac{4}{5}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\beta_x=\frac{\tfrac{4}{5}}{\gamma}
=\frac{4/5}{5/3}
=\frac{4}{5}\cdot\frac{3}{5}
=\frac{12}{25},
$$
$$
\Lambda^0_{\ 2}=-\gamma\,\beta_y=-\frac{16}{15}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
\beta_y=\frac{\tfrac{16}{15}}{\gamma}
=\frac{16/15}{5/3}
=\frac{16}{15}\cdot\frac{3}{5}
=\frac{16}{25},
$$
且 $\beta_z=0$。
3. 模为
$$
|\beta|=\sqrt{\beta_x^2+\beta_y^2}
=\sqrt{\frac{144}{625}+\frac{256}{625}}
=\sqrt{\frac{400}{625}}
=\frac{4}{5}\,.
$$
4. 因此，单位矢量的分量为
$$
\hat\beta_x=\frac{\beta_x}{|\beta|}
=\frac{\tfrac{12}{25}}{\tfrac{4}{5}}
=\frac{12}{25}\cdot\frac{5}{4}
=\frac{3}{5}\,.
$$
